a href=\"/feedback\">Let us know what you think!</a></p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!-- / .firstset -->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"four columns first\">\r\n	<h2>Community</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns second\">\r\n	<div class=\"learningmodule\">\r\n		<h3><a href=\"/members\">Members</a></h3>\r\n		<p>Browse the <a href=\"/members\">profiles</a> of people who have joined this site. Find members with similar <a href=\"/tags\">interests</a>.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns third\">\r\n	<div class=\"learningmodule\">\r\n		<h3><a href=\"/members/contributors\">Contributors</a></h3>\r\n		<p>Curious who has done what? Browse the <a href=\"/members/contributors\">profiles</a> of Members who have contributed <a href=\"/resources\">resources</a>.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns fourth\">\r\n	<div class=\"group\">\r\n		<h3><a href=\"/groups\">Groups</a></h3>\r\n		<p>Members working together. Explore our <a href=\"/groups\">groups</a> and get in touch with <a href=\"/members\">members</a> with similar interests.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"four columns first\">\r\n	<h2>Services</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns second\">\r\n	<div class=\"contribute\">\r\n		<h3><a href=\"/contribute\">Upload</a></h3>\r\n		<p><a href=\"/contribute\">Publish</a> your own tools, seminars, and other content on this site.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns third\">\r\n	<div class=\"tool\">\r\n		<h3><a href=\"/tools\">Tool Forge</a></h3>\r\n		<p>The <a href=\"/tools\">development area</a> for simulation tools. Sign up and manage your own software project!</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns fourth\">\r\n	<div class=\"donate\">\r\n		<h3><a href=\"/store\">Store</a></h3>\r\n		<p><a href=\"/store\">Purchase items</a> such as t-shirts using points you earn by helping out.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"four columns first\">\r\n	<h2>What\'s Happening</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns second\">\r\n	<div class=\"note\">\r\n		<h3><a href=\"/events\">Events</a></h3>\r\n		<p>Find information about the many upcoming <a href=\"/events\">public meetings and scientific symposia</a>.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns third\">\r\n	<div class=\"workshop\">\r\n		<h3><a href=\"/whatsnew\">What\'s New</a></h3>\r\n		<p>Find the latest content posted on the site with our <a href=\"/whatsnew\">What\'s New</a> section.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns fourth\">\r\n	<div class=\"group\">\r\n		<h3><a href=\"/xpoll\">Community Poll</a></h3>\r\n		<p>Respond to our poll questions and <a href=\"/xpoll\">see what everyone else is thinking</a>.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>','',1,0,0,0,'NOW()',62,'','NOW()',62,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','NOW()','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','','show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=0\nshow_create_date=0\nshow_modify_date=0\nshow_pdf_icon=0\nshow_print_icon=0\nshow_email_icon=0\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=',6,0,2,'','',0,55,'robots=\nauthor=');
